title: Ala Gal (minimalistic mix)
info:
Remix of Charles Deenen's remix called Ala Gal which is a remix of Neil Baldwin's Demonic 1

Lyrics:
Nothing's right, and nothing's wrong
You feel you can grow, grow so strong
And you wish, wish you had known the world
any better, but now talk no more...
Blurred, just faded, dying youth crusade in me
Always underestimated, worthless,
Like a tear in your eye,
You're in pain but can't cry
You know this is goodbye...
